in client add username and password
the authetification messages will be sent from server
on server side check the combination
if correct - its all good
if incorrect - refuse connection
(
    security - count incorrect attempts; upon succes turn to zero, ban time to None
    if incorrect amount higher save ban time;
    if ban time is something and lower than 5 minutes, don't allow
)
if .new-user - start a new user - add to user table (in broadcasting task)

on read_from_socket add messages message table

on accepting task send the whole chat history to client and print it there
